  "texts": [
    "• Knowledge-based Retrieval.",
    "This paradigm further improves retrieval accuracy and interpretability by integrating domain-specific knowledge into the retrieval process [39], [61].",
    "For instance, Heuillet et al. [61] improve retrieval precision and reasoning robustness by fusing structured knowledge graphs with dense vector retrieval within a RAG framework.",
    "However, traditional RAG systems are limited by static workflows and lack the adaptability for multi-step reasoning and complex task management.",
    "• Agentic-enhanced Retrieval."
  ]
